o\": 357}, {\"ngram\": \"event\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"Evening Standard\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourprivacy notice\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 422}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the angular surroundings of BaySixty6, beneath the busy Westway flyover,Sky Brownhas just finished pulling all kinds of skate tricks forES Magazine'sphotographer.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 484, \"end\": 491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Side_Highway\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8819073633189143e-36, \"text\": \"Westway\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Side_Highway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Side_Highway\"}, {\"begin\": 500, \"end\": 503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999560742897005, \"rank\": 4.392764002808761e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the angular surroundings\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 452}, {\"ngram\": \"BaySixty6\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 465}, {\"ngram\": \"all kinds\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"skate tricks\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 560}, {\"ngram\": \"forES Magazine'sphotographer\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, dressed down in cargo trousers and a Nike hoodie, she's ready to chill.\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 633, \"end\": 637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9965556641709495, \"rank\": 0.0034562402655807507, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cargo trousers\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But first she needs to pee.\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 695, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pee\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The UK's youngest-ever Olympic medallist is faced with a choice: there are no women's toilets, only men's and a disabled cubicle.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 825, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 700, \"end\": 702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_English\", \"score\": 0.9315533372444161, \"rank\": 0.0714144823273512, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_English\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_English\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a choice\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 759}, {\"ngram\": \"no women's toilets\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She opts for the disabled.\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The most exciting female in British skating is on her home turf, and somehow she's still out of place.\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 881, \"end\": 888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9834437346225446, \"rank\": 0.016834963983928707, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The most exciting female\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"her home turf\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Feeling out of place, though, is Sky Brown's homeostasis.\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 990, \"end\": 999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sky Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 977}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her life is lined with the stretch marks of being first in her field.\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her life\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1023}, {\"ngram\": \"the stretch marks\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1055}, {\"ngram\": \"her field\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In headlines, her name is nearly always followed by the phrase 'youngest ever', from taking part in the Vans US Open aged eight, to earning a Nike sponsorship aged 11, to qualifying for the Tokyo Olympics aged 13.\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1227, \"end\": 1231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9965556641709495, \"rank\": 0.0034562402655807507, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"headlines\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"her name\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1107}, {\"ngram\": \"the phrase\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1147}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1181}, {\"ngram\": \"the Vans\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\": \"US Open\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1289}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her most recent accolade was a gold medal at the 2023 WorldSkateboardingChampionships, making her the first British world champion in history.\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1441, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her most recent accolade\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2023 WorldSkateboardingChampionships\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She rubs shoulders with the greats, texting Avril Lavigne and training with snowboarder Shaun White.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1542, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1486, \"end\": 1499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avril_Lavigne\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.563727684645451e-71, \"text\": \"Avril Lavigne\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avril_Lavigne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avril_Lavigne\"}, {\"begin\": 1530, \"end\": 1541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaun_White\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shaun White\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaun_White\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaun_White\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"shoulders\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1460}, {\"ngram\": \"the greats\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2021, skateboarding legend Tony Hawk described Sky as 'one of the best female skaters ever, if not one of the best wellrounded skaters ever, regardless of gender'.\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1593, \"end\": 1596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999560742897005, \"rank\": 4.392764002808761e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"skateboarding legend Tony Hawk\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"the best female skaters\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"the best wellrounded skaters\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1680}, {\"ngram\": \"gender\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite her highly decorated status and increasingly recognisable profile, Sky, now 15, says she still gets 'the look' from boys at the skate park.\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1786, \"end\": 1789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999560742897005, \"rank\": 4.392764002808761e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her highly decorated status\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1746}, {\"ngram\": \"increasingly recognisable profile\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1784}, {\"ngram\": \"the look\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1828}, {\"ngram\": \"boys\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"the skate park\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1857}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's like, \\\"Why is she here?\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why is this little girl here?\\\"'\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this little girl\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"she explains, sitting cross-legged in front of me in the skate shop of BaySixty6.\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 2002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1964}, {\"ngram\": \"the skate shop\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1988}, {\"ngram\": \"BaySixty6\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have been around [skating] since I was really tiny, I was this little girl showing up at the skate park.\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this little girl\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2080}, {\"ngram\": \"the skate park\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And of course these big boys are going to look at me, but honestly - I just want to show them what's up.\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2215, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2124}, {\"ngram\": \"these big boys\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2139}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If they give me that look, it just makes me pumped up.'\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To be fair, when the world was first introduced to the always-smiling, relentlessly optimistic force of nature that is Sky Brown, she was still a little girl.\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2392, \"end\": 2401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sky Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2299}, {\"ngram\": \"the always-smiling, relentlessly optimistic force\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"nature\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"a little girl\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many discovered her in 2019, when the then-10-year-old announced that she would be joining Great Britain for the Tokyo 2020 Olympics.\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2565, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Great Britain\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2536}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo 2020 Olympics\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taught to skate by her father, Stuart, at a young age, Sky forced her way on to the board more than she found it.\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2679, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2597, \"end\": 2603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuart_Neilson\", \"score\": 0.6694576769770895, \"rank\": 0.4656687808925061, \"text\": \"Stuart\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuart_Neilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuart_Neilson\"}, {\"begin\": 2621, \"end\": 2624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999560742897005, \"rank\": 4.392764002808761e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her father\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2595}, {\"ngram\": \"a young age\", \"from\": 2608, \"to\": 2619}, {\"ngram\": \"her way\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2639}, {\"ngram\": \"the board\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I watched him and stole his board,' Sky laughs, 'he did not want me to because that was his thing.\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2717, \"end\": 2720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999560742897005, \"rank\": 4.392764002808761e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his board\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2714}, {\"ngram\": \"his thing\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2778}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I still ended up stealing it.'\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When young, skate-obsessed Sky would not give up, so Stuart decided he might as well coach her.\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2910, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2842, \"end\": 2845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999560742897005, \"rank\": 4.392764002808761e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 2868, \"end\": 2874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuart_Neilson\", \"score\": 0.6694576769770895, \"rank\": 0.4656687808925061, \"text\": \"Stuart\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuart_Neilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuart_Neilson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And anything he could not teach, she learnt through YouTube - when she wasn't busy watching make-up tutorials like any of her peers.\", \"from\": 2911, \"to\": 3043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2963, \"end\": 2970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"score\": 0.9999999998690328, \"rank\": 1.312992775243236e-10, \"text\": \"YouTube\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"make-up tutorials\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3020}, {\"ngram\": \"her peers\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now she beams just as brightly as she when she was 10, but there is something else at play, too.\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3141, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3122}, {\"ngram\": \"play\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have more fire in me than ever,' she says confidently.\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3199, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more fire\", \"from\": 3150, \"to\": 3159}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This becomes clear when I probe her about those boys who give her 'the look'.\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3277, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those boys\", \"from\": 3242, \"to\": 3252}, {\"ngram\": \"the look\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I like to show them my power - like, I like to go high, higher than the boys,' she grins.\", \"from\": 3278, \"to\": 3368, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the boys\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I like to grind longer than the boys... tweak it harder than the boys.\", \"from\": 3369, \"to\": 3440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the boys\", \"from\": 3398, \"to\": 3406}, {\"ngram\": \"the boys\", \"from\": 3431, \"to\": 3439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And because my style is making it look beautiful, to make it look prettier than the boys.'\", \"from\": 3441, \"to\": 3531, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my style\", \"from\": 3453, \"to\": 3461}, {\"ngram\": \"the boys\", \"from\": 3521, \"to\": 3529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sky's decision to join Team GB in 2019 came as a slight surprise: up until this point, it was assumed she would be opting for the Japanese team.\", \"from\": 3533, \"to\": 3677, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3533, \"end\": 3536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999560742897005, \"rank\": 4.392764002808761e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 3556, \"end\": 3563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.99999999974807, \"rank\": 2.5206675151971425e-10, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 3663, \"end\": 3671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9999998330895462, \"rank\": 1.6685520992217807e-07, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a slight surprise\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3597}, {\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her father is British, but her mother, Meiko, is Japanese and Sky grew up primarily between Miyazaki, on the Japanese island of Kyushu, and California.\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3717, \"end\": 3722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meiko_Scientific\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9018891546361268e-20, \"text\": \"Meiko\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meiko_Scientific\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meiko_Scientific\"}, {\"begin\": 3740, \"end\": 3743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999560742897005, \"rank\": 4.392764002808761e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 3770, \"end\": 3778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hayao_Miyazaki\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.3933504063694435e-12, \"text\": \"Miyazaki\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hayao_Miyazaki\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hayao_Miyazaki\"}, {\"begin\": 3787, \"end\": 3795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9999998330895462, \"rank\": 1.6685520992217807e-07, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3806, \"end\": 3812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyushu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.566831732708838e-16, \"text\": \"Kyushu\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyushu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyushu\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her father\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3688}, {\"ngram\": \"her mother\", \"from\": 3705, \"to\": 3715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the lack of the Queen's English, she insists that she's British in her own small ways: she loves a curry, a pie and a fry-up, and she's even recently come around to the concept of baked beans.\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 4030, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lack\", \"from\": 3838, \"to\": 3846}, {\"ngram\": \"the Queen's English\", \"from\": 3850, \"to\": 3869}, {\"ngram\": \"her own small ways\", \"from\": 3905, \"to\": 3923}, {\"ngram\": \"a curry\", \"from\": 3935, \"to\": 3942}, {\"ngram\": \"a pie\", \"from\": 3944, \"to\": 3949}, {\"ngram\": \"a fry-up\", \"from\": 3954, \"to\": 3962}, {\"ngram\": \"the concept\", \"from\": 4003, \"to\": 4014}, {\"ngram\": \"baked beans\", \"from\": 4018, \"to\": 4029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'[Britain] definitely feels like one of my homes now,' she says.\", \"from\": 4031, \"to\": 4095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4033, \"end\": 4040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999997402286417, \"rank\": 2.5977201872893204e-06, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my homes\", \"from\": 4071, \"to\": 4079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I come here a lot and every time I do it feels like home.'\", \"from\": 4096, \"to\": 4155, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every time\", \"from\": 4119, \"to\": 4129}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 4149, \"to\": 4153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's not quite up-to-date on the slang - peng and clapped leave her puzzled - but she does occasionally throw a wholly authentic 'gosh' into conversation.\", \"from\": 4156, \"to\": 4311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"date\", \"from\": 4178, \"to\": 4182}, {\"ngram\": \"the slang - peng\", \"from\": 4186, \"to\": 4202}, {\"ngram\": \"her puzzled\", \"from\": 4221, \"to\": 4232}, {\"ngram\": \"conversation\", \"from\": 4298, \"to\": 4310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sky took home a bronze medal for Great Britain at the Tokyo Olympics in 2021 at the age of 13.\", \"from\": 4313, \"to\": 4407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4313, \"end\": 4316, \"title\