"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tough watch\", \"from\": 4973, \"to\": 4986}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 4991, \"to\": 4997}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 5009, \"to\": 5016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her family did not want her to skate any more.\", \"from\": 5031, \"to\": 5077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her family\", \"from\": 5031, \"to\": 5041}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They did not even want her to watch the video, let alone post it online.\", \"from\": 5078, \"to\": 5150, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 5114, \"to\": 5123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she thought it looked cool, and she stands by that.\", \"from\": 5151, \"to\": 5206, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Oh definitely, I still think it looks cool.\", \"from\": 5207, \"to\": 5251, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's part of my story.\", \"from\": 5252, \"to\": 5274, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 5257, \"to\": 5261}, {\"ngram\": \"my story\", \"from\": 5265, \"to\": 5273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Looking back, it definitely was a scary moment and\\u2026 it hurted!'\", \"from\": 5275, \"to\": 5338, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a scary moment\", \"from\": 5307, \"to\": 5321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"she jokes, a reference to an old skateboarding Vine video from seven years ago.\", \"from\": 5339, \"to\": 5418, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5386, \"end\": 5390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vine\", \"score\": 0.9999999777091946, \"rank\": 2.229088004004833e-08, \"text\": \"Vine\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a reference\", \"from\": 5350, \"to\": 5361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But it just made me stronger, it made me who I am today.'\", \"from\": 5419, \"to\": 5477, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Convincing her family to let her back on the board wasn't easy.\", \"from\": 5479, \"to\": 5542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her family\", \"from\": 5490, \"to\": 5500}, {\"ngram\": \"the board\", \"from\": 5520, \"to\": 5529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sky's mother completely lost the ability to watch her skate live, and had to instead watch replays of her competitions.\", \"from\": 5543, \"to\": 5662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5543, \"end\": 5546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999560742897005, \"rank\": 4.392764002808761e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ability\", \"from\": 5572, \"to\": 5583}, {\"ngram\": \"her skate\", \"from\": 5593, \"to\": 5602}, {\"ngram\": \"replays\", \"from\": 5634, \"to\": 5641}, {\"ngram\": \"her competitions\", \"from\": 5645, \"to\": 5661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'She was definitely having a hard time,' Sky says of her mum.\", \"from\": 5663, \"to\": 5724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5704, \"end\": 5707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999560742897005, \"rank\": 4.392764002808761e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hard time\", \"from\": 5690, \"to\": 5701}, {\"ngram\": \"her mum\", \"from\": 5716, \"to\": 5723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I mean, she's still scared to watch me but she will cheer me on, always.'\", \"from\": 5725, \"to\": 5799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sky's father, Stuart, had less of a leg to stand on because he was the person who got her into skating in the first place.\", \"from\": 5800, \"to\": 5922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5800, \"end\": 5803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999560742897005, \"rank\": 4.392764002808761e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 5814, \"end\": 5820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuart_Neilson\", \"score\": 0.6694576769770895, \"rank\": 0.4656687808925061, \"text\": \"Stuart\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuart_Neilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuart_Neilson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a leg\", \"from\": 5834, \"to\": 5839}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 5867, \"to\": 5877}, {\"ngram\": \"skating\", \"from\": 5895, \"to\": 5902}, {\"ngram\": \"the first place\", \"from\": 5906, \"to\": 5921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So when Sky wanted to get straight back on the board - 'It was pretty easy,' she says nonchalantly - Stuart had no choice but to continue what he'd started.\", \"from\": 5923, \"to\": 6079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5931, \"end\": 5934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999560742897005, \"rank\": 4.392764002808761e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the board\", \"from\": 5966, \"to\": 5975}, {\"ngram\": \"- Stuart\", \"from\": 6022, \"to\": 6030}, {\"ngram\": \"no choice\", \"from\": 6035, \"to\": 6044}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair went back into training and secured Sky her bronze medal.\", \"from\": 6080, \"to\": 6146, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6125, \"end\": 6128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999560742897005, \"rank\": 4.39276