me, prompting the family to move.\", \"from\": 6345, \"to\": 6623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6577, \"end\": 6587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.9999999602468969, \"rank\": 3.972557419540006e-08, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 6349, \"to\": 6356}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 6444, \"to\": 6456}, {\"ngram\": \"her celebrity\", \"from\": 6458, \"to\": 6471}, {\"ngram\": \"a level\", \"from\": 6480, \"to\": 6487}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 6497, \"to\": 6503}, {\"ngram\": \"gifts\", \"from\": 6549, \"to\": 6554}, {\"ngram\": \"cards\", \"from\": 6559, \"to\": 6564}, {\"ngram\": \"the family\", \"from\": 6604, \"to\": 6614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her hobby officially became her work.\", \"from\": 6624, \"to\": 6661, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her hobby\", \"from\": 6624, \"to\": 6633}, {\"ngram\": \"her work\", \"from\": 6652, \"to\": 6660}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At this point, she says, she's done more interviews and photo shoots than she can count.\", \"from\": 6662, \"to\": 6750, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 6665, \"to\": 6675}, {\"ngram\": \"more interviews\", \"from\": 6698, \"to\": 6713}, {\"ngram\": \"photo shoots\", \"from\": 6718, \"to\": 6730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I ask her for a ballpark figure.\", \"from\": 6751, \"to\": 6783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a ballpark figure\", \"from\": 6765, \"to\": 6782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She genuinely can not name one.\", \"from\": 6784, \"to\": 6815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the joy is still there.\", \"from\": 6816, \"to\": 6843, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the joy\", \"from\": 6820, \"to\": 6827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The language she uses around her professional sport is still that of fun: the board is her 'toy', the skate park is her 'playground'.\", \"from\": 6844, \"to\": 6977, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The language\", \"from\": 6844, \"to\": 6856}, {\"ngram\": \"her professional sport\", \"from\": 6873, \"to\": 6895}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 6913, \"to\": 6916}, {\"ngram\": \"the board\", \"from\": 6918, \"to\": 6927}, {\"ngram\": \"toy\", \"from\": 6936, \"to\": 6939}, {\"ngram\": \"the skate park\", \"from\": 6942, \"to\": 6956}, {\"ngram\": \"her 'playground\", \"from\": 6960, \"to\": 6975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It definitely does not feel like work, she says.\", \"from\": 6978, \"to\": 7026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 7011, \"to\": 7015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I just want to put on a show.\", \"from\": 7027, \"to\": 7057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a show\", \"from\": 7050, \"to\": 7056}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to make people excited to watch me, to see the beauty in skating.'\", \"from\": 7058, \"to\": 7131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 7073, \"to\": 7079}, {\"ngram\": \"the beauty\", \"from\": 7108, \"to\": 7118}, {\"ngram\": \"skating\", \"from\": 7122, \"to\": 7129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, she only wants to do more.\", \"from\": 7133, \"to\": 7168, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 7136, \"to\": 7140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, Sky entered for both skateboarding and surfing at theParis Olympics, and was clear on stating her hopes to win a medal in both.\", \"from\": 7169, \"to\": 7307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7180, \"end\": 7183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999560742897005, \"rank\": 4.392764002808761e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympics\", \"from\": 7230, \"to\": 7247}, {\"ngram\": \"her hopes\", \"from\": 7274, \"to\": 7283}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 7291, \"to\": 7298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She sadly failed to qualify for surfing, missing out by one place, but is not giving up any time soon.\", \"from\": 7308, \"to\": 7410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"surfing\", \"from\": 7340, \"to\": 7347}, {\"ngram\": \"one place\", \"from\": 7364, \"to\": 7373}, {\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 7396, \"to\": 7404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was a little bit of a bummer,' she says, 'but I am always going to be surfing.'\", \"from\": 7411, \"to\": 7494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 7419, \"to\": 7431}, {\"ngram\": \"a bummer\", \"from\": 7435, \"to\": 7443}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I ask her what she'd be if she were not an athlete, she tells me assuredly she 'would have always found [her] way into the water'.\", \"from\": 7495, \"to\": 7630, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 7540, \"to\": 7550}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 7619, \"to\": 7628}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Are you suffering from Burnout this Blue Monday?\", \"from\": 7632, \"to\": 7680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Burnout\", \"from\": 7655, \"to\": 7662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Take this quiz to find out What jeans should we be wearing now?\", \"from\": 7681, \"to\": 7745, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this quiz\", \"from\": 7686, \"to\": 7695}, {\"ngram\": \"What jeans\", \"from\": 7708, \"to\": 7718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The philosopher who says big tech has got superintelligence wrong Is coffee the future of socialising?\", \"from\": 7747, \"to\": 7850, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The philosopher\", \"from\": 7747, \"to\": 7762}, {\"ngram\": \"big tech\", \"from\": 7772, \"to\": 7780}, {\"ngram\": \"superintelligence\", \"from\": 7789, \"to\": 7806}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 7823, \"to\": 7833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This stylish spot thinks so For Sky, it's a way of life.\", \"from\": 7851, \"to\": 7908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7884, \"end\": 7887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999560742897005, \"rank\": 4.392764002808761e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This stylish spot\", \"from\": 7851, \"to\": 7868}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 7893, \"to\": 7898}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 7902, \"to\": 7906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her speech is littered with skate terminology and slang, and during our photo shoot she takes every opportunity to get her feet off the cold English concrete and on to her board.\", \"from\": 7909, \"to\": 8087, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her speech\", \"from\": 7909, \"to\": 7919}, {\"ngram\": \"skate terminology\", \"from\": 7937, \"to\": 7954}, {\"ngram\": \"slang\", \"from\": 7959, \"to\": 7964}, {\"ngram\": \"our photo shoot\", \"from\": 7977, \"to\": 7992}, {\"ngram\": \"every opportunity\", \"from\": 8003, \"to\": 8020}, {\"ngram\": \"her feet\", \"from\": 8028, \"to\": 8036}, {\"ngram\": \"the cold English concrete\", \"from\": 8041, \"to\": 8066}, {\"ngram\": \"her board\", \"from\": 8077, \"to\": 8086}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's also been imbued with a love of skate culture.\", \"from\": 8088, \"to\": 8140, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a love\", \"from\": 8116, \"to\": 8122}, {\"ngram\": \"skate culture\", \"from\": 8126, \"to\": 8139}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sure, she might be a little young for the likes of Kids or Street Dreams but she was raised watching Lords of Dogtown and listening to pop-punk queen Avril Lavigne, after whom Stuart jokes they almost named Sky.\", \"from\": 8141, \"to\": 8352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8251, \"end\": 8258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dogtown_and_Z-Boys\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.37127144562531e-33, \"text\": \"Dogtown\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dogtown_and_Z-Boys\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dogtown_and_Z-Boys\"}, {\"begin\": 8348, \"end\": 8351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999560742897005, \"rank\": 4.392764002808761e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the likes\", \"from\": 8179, \"to\": 8188}, {\"ngram\": \"Kids\", \"from\": 8192, \"to\": 8196}, {\"ngram\": \"Street Dreams\", \"from\": 8200, \"to\": 8213}, {\"ngram\": \"Lords\", \"from\": 8242, \"to\": 8247}, {\"ngram\": \"Stuart\", \"from\": 8317, \"to\": 8323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though Lavigne's hit 'Sk8er Boi' was released six years before Sky was even born, she still sees her as a skating icon to this day.\", \"from\": 8353, \"to\": 8489, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8421, \"end\": 8424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999560742897005, \"rank\": 4.392764002808761e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lavigne's hit 'Sk8er Boi\", \"from\": 8365, \"to\": 8389}, {\"ngram\": \"a skating icon\", \"from\": 8462, \"to\": 8476}, {\"ngram\": \"this day\", \"from\": 8480, \"to\": 8488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'She is one of my idols,' Sky says, 'she's really sweet, we are still talking and she sent me a signed board that says \\\"skater girl\\\".\", \"from\": 8490, \"to\": 8623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8516, \"end\"